targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  lap AS "Lap"
FROM 
  $Event 
WHERE 
  session = $Session 
GROUP BY 
  lap 
ORDER BY 
  MAX(elapsed_time)
LIMIT 1;

SELECT 
  MAX(speed) AS top_speed 
FROM
  $Event 
WHERE 
  session = $Session;

SELECT 
  MAX(power_level) AS max_power_level 
FROM 
  $Event
WHERE
  session = $Session;

SELECT 
    sub.state_of_charge,
    v.estimated_voltage,
    (sub.power_level * 1000) / v.estimated_voltage AS estimated_amps
FROM (
    SELECT state_of_charge, power_level
    FROM $Event
    WHERE session = $Session
    AND power_level = (
        SELECT MAX(power_level)
        FROM $Event
        WHERE session = $Session
    )
) AS sub,
LATERAL (
    SELECT 
        CASE 
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 100 THEN 462
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 95 THEN 458.7
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 90 THEN 456.5
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 85 THEN 451
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 80 THEN 445.5
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 75 THEN 440
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 70 THEN 434.5
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 65 THEN 429
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 60 THEN 423.5
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 55 THEN 418
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 50 THEN 412.5
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 45 THEN 407
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 40 THEN 401.5
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 35 THEN 396
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 30 THEN 390.5
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 25 THEN 385
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 20 THEN 379.5
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 15 THEN 374
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 10 THEN 363
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 5 THEN 352
            WHEN sub.state_of_charge >= 0 THEN 330  
        END AS estimated_voltage
) v;

SELECT

  $Event
WHERE
  session = $Session AND lap = '1';

SELECT
  to_char(to_timestamp(MAX(elapsed_time) / 1000.0), 'MI:SS.MS') AS "Lap Time"
FROM 
  $Event 
WHERE 
  session = $Session 
GROUP BY 
  lap 
ORDER BY 
  "Lap Time" 
LIMIT 1;
